  "description": "Boutique Chain showcase for Foundation mood. OSTERIA's Porto Wine warmth (low-mid resonance from the ShoreSystem) through Boutique Chain at maximum-weight settings. Anomaly TextureBlend 0.4 and ReverbSize 0.70 (large initial spatial context). Dissolving Archive Chance 0.10 and Dissolve 0.30 (long-lasting memories) — old material resurfaces rarely but persists. Cathedral DarkMix 0.85 (maximum darkness), Decay 0.85 (very long reverb). Submersion 6 stages, LFORate 0.08 Hz — extremely slow rotation. The combined effect is OSTERIA as the foundation of an ancient archive: warm, dark, deep, with occasional unexpected retrievals from the past.",
